_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice D'Amato\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italy'sAlice D'Amatowon balance beam gold as afalldoomed US gymnastics greatSimone Biles'sbid for a record five gold medals at theParis Olympicson Monday.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7223373382434414, \"rank\": 0.37542835386933615, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, who led the US women to team gold before claiming the all-around and vault titles, was among several finalists to fall off the unforgiving apparatus.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7223373382434414, \"rank\": 0.37542835386933615, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the seven-time Olympic gold medallist still has a chance to take her overall tally to eight with a fourth Paris gold in floor exercise later on Monday.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4943787319644658e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  Meanwhile, D'Amato, with a score of 14.366, celebrated a first ever women's gymnastics gold for Italy, who also sawManila Espositotake bronze behind China'sZhou Yuqin.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6503144391830435, \"rank\": 0.5200050201637546, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9997563804614141, \"rank\": 0.0002395207024773977, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just how treacherous the 10cm wide beam can be was clear when the first three starters made big mistakes.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's world silver medallist Zhou lost her balance and had to touch the beam to avoid coming off.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9997563804614141, \"rank\": 0.0002395207024773977, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"w